creator: Nedap Staffing Solutions
descriptionHtml:
The PEP App was created for everyone that arranges their work business via PEP! The PEP App is accessible for you as a flex worker, if your staffing agency has given you a PEP account. Your staffing agency will let you know when the app is available for you.

What can I do with the PEP App?

- View my registered hours
- Keep in touch with my intermediary by sending and receiving messages
- Respond directly to pick up extra shifts
- Receive notifications of messages

descriptionHtml: In the Flux app you indicate when you can work.  You will then receive the planning and when your work is done, you register your worked hours. All from the Flux app. This way you always have an overview of your leave balance and other balances.
descriptionShort: The app for your planning and time registrations
